snippet.title: Nanoui Trailer
snippet.description:
Get it now on Steam!! http://store.steampowered.com/app/809080/Nanoui/?yt
 
The book of Nanoui has been stolen, plunging the kingdom into chaos and allowing the forces of evil to rise. Set in a fantasy world of great castles, magic and dragons, our four heroes begin their quest to retrieve the powerful artifact and save the kingdom.
Up to four friends can join forces and play locally or online, to hack and slash your way to victory through hordes of ghouls, trolls, demons, spiders and many more.

Website : http://www.phoesion.com/nanoui
Steam : http://store.steampowered.com/app/809080/Nanoui/yt

Intro Effects : http://www.ravenprodesign.co
